Home » News » Entertainment » TV » Guest lineups for the… Guest lineups for the Sunday news shows By The Associated Press October 2, 2015 9:02 pm 
WASHINGTON (AP) — Guest lineups for the Sunday TV news shows: 
ABC’s “This Week” — Republican presidential candidates Donald Trump and Chris Christie; Reps. Tom Cole, R-Okla., and Keith Ellison, D-Minn. 
___ 
NBC’s “Meet the Press” — Trump. 
___ 
CBS’“Face the Nation” — Pre-empted by NFL coverage. 
___ 
CNN’s “State of the Union” — Sens. Elizabeth Warren, D-Mass., and John McCain, R-Ariz.; Rep. Marsha Blackburn, R-Tenn. 
___ 
“Fox News Sunday” — Rep. Jason Chaffetz, R-Utah. Topics:
